      "role": "user",
      "content": "it's a lot more than just \"focus\" though. it feels structural. like my neurons are literally firing differently. i was reading about how certain cosmic radiation events can actually trigger epigenetic shifts or rapid mutations in DNA... do you think it’s possible that high-energy particles hitting us could actually trigger a biological \"upgrade\" like that?",
